1113, "(fr)The Siren is the replacement for the Great War-era Interceptor missile. This aspect-seeking weapon uses a more durable missile head to improve its ability to pierce hulls and shields. The Siren also has superior speed and maneuverability when compared to the Interceptor. Many of its improvements were made thanks to the sharing of research and technology with the Vasudans."
