1109, "(fr)The Interceptor is an aspect-seeking weapon that currently serves as the baseline dogfighting missile in both the GTA and PVN. With an ample payload and enough maneuverability to pursue enemy targets, the only chief vulnerability the Interceptor has is its ability to be misled by countermeasures."
