1595, "(fr)The Tsunami anti-cruiser bomb is the baseline anti-warship weapon of the GTA and PVN. Having been developed during the early stages of the Shivan Incursion, the Tsunami was an essential tool for answering the dreaded Shivan Lilith, and was also effective in interdicting Shivan logistics. The Tsunami has seen some limited success in attacking destroyers, but the powerful Harbinger is still preferred for attacking these massive ships.<br/><br/>Work is underway to reverse-engineer the GTI Serkr bomb as a replacement for the aging Tsunami."
