10640, "(fr)LNA engineers originally developed the Torche Ionique as a hardened variation of the standard ion engine found on most small craft. The intent was for the engine to serve as means by which transports and mining drones could avoid costly repairs at the hand of the unstable radiation of the Hellstars emanating from the core of the system. While advances in sensor technology and shield tuning made the engine obsolete, particularly bold LNA engineers drastically amplified the power of the engine, turning it into a powerful cutting beam of raw ionic energy capable of burning through hulls and shields alike. The Torche Ionique also functions as a sort of reverse afterburner when fired, sending the ship firing it backwards or slowing it down. This weapon is perfect for pilots who like to fight up close and personal."
