10886, "(fr)Congratulations! You've passed the tutorial, and now you know everything you need to know to enjoy Between the Ashes. Enter the campaign room and select one of our campaigns. We recommend starting with Mefistofele, a pair of missions staring a pirate with an unexpected impact on the larger story."
10887, "(fr)Welcome to Between the Ashes. This project has been a labor of love spanning many years, and everyone involves hopes you'll enjoy it.<br/><br/>If this is your first experience with Freespace, you've come to the right place. If you'd like to learn more about our world, feel free to visit the tech room. Otherwise, enter the ready room for a playable tutorial. If you have played Freespace before, we suggest selecting Mefistofele in the campaign room."
