11068, "(fr)!html Welcome to <span class='white'>Simulated Combat Session SCS-1-<span>Gamma<$slashspan><$slashspan>. This simulator module is provided on an experimental basis and HAS NOT been approved by the Galactic Terran Alliance. In this module, you will fly a simulation of the GTF Valkyrie intercept fighter.

The Valkyrie is typically employed as a convoy escort, destroying enemy bombs and bombers before they can reach their targets. However, its high maneuverability and powerful reactor make it equally adept at surgical strikes to destroy enemy warship turrets. You will practice both roles today while escorting a simulated GTC Fenris-class strike cruiser. You will also learn how to request rearm and repair in battle.

Commit to the simulation when ready."
