11212, "(fr)!html Welcome to <span class='white'>Simulated Combat Session SCS-2-<span>Alpha<$slashspan><$slashspan>. This simulator module is provided on an experimental basis and HAS NOT been approved by the Galactic Terran Alliance. In this module, you will learn to coordinate with allied assets in battle. I will act as your wingmate in a simulated convoy escort.

