11213, "(fr)!html You have completed <span class='white'>Simulated Combat Session SCS-2-<span>Alpha<$slashspan><$slashspan>. Your success in this operation means you may have a future in command. Well done. If you would like to repeat this simulation, you may schedule additional simulator time from your terminal in the barracks. Otherwise, report to your ready room to begin briefing for the next simulation."
11214, "(fr)!html A convoy ship was destroyed by enemy action. As a pilot of the Galactic Terran Alliance, you will often be called upon to provide escort for Allied assets. Consider how different command decisions may have lead to a different outcome. You have failed this session, but may repeat it when you feel you are ready."
11215, "(fr)Try splitting your forces. Send some fighters (maybe including yourself) to engage the pirate as they jump in, while the rest stay with the convoy."
