11253, "(fr)!html Welcome to <span class='white'>Simulated Combat Session SCS-2-<span>Bêta<$slashspan><$slashspan>. This simulator module is provided on an experimental basis and HAS NOT been approved by the Galactic Terran Alliance. In this module, you will fight waves of enemy strikecraft and practice your combat skills.

Unlike previous sessions, you may choose your loadout for this simulation. Select <span class='white'>Ship Selection</span> or <span class='white'>Weapon Selection</span> to do so.

Commit to the simulation when ready."
11254, "Escadrilles Ennemies"
